Class ScriptableMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.mozilla.javascript.ScriptableObject
      • org.apache.sling.scripting.javascript.wrapper.ScriptableBase
        • org.apache.sling.scripting.javascript.wrapper.ScriptableMap
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, SlingWrapper, org.mozilla.javascript.ConstProperties, org.mozilla.javascript.debug.DebuggableObject, org.mozilla.javascript.Scriptable, org.mozilla.javascript.Wrapper

    public class ScriptableMap
extends ScriptableBase
implements SlingWrapper
    The ScriptableMap wrapper provides easier access to a map's values by setting the map's keys as properties to the JavaScript object representing the Map.
